title: FROM 2018: Elizabeth Olsen (Avengers/Dr. Strange)
itunes:title: FROM 2018: Elizabeth Olsen (Avengers/Dr. Strange)
description:
Danny throws it back to one of the very first guests ever on Everything Iconic, Elizabeth Olsen! Elizabeth stars in Dr. Strange 2, out now on Disney+, and when she stopped by the podcast back in 2018, she and Danny talked about Scarlett Witch, her sisters, Housewives, and so much more!
